{"tid":2369565,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香蕉病大流行引發絕種危機","createTime":"2021-01-17T09:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T10:57:41.000Z","uid":100150,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7c0c72b741278658db655e9d6002969a62782842","tid":2369565,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://external.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/safe_image.php?d=AQECVRHDhnkn1eqU&amp;w=500&amp;h=261&amp;url=fbstaging%3A%2F%2Fgraph.facebook.com%2Fstaging_resources%2FMDE4NDU5MTI3NDI5MTcwNTE6NjM4NDI4MDU%3D&amp;cfs=1&amp;ext=jpg&amp;_nc_cb=1&amp;_nc_hash=AQHGXmyyiZW2XlGs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexternal.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fsafe_image.php%3Fd%3DAQECVRHDhnkn1eqU%26w%3D500%26h%3D261%26url%3Dfbstaging%253A%252F%252Fgraph.facebook.com%252Fstaging_resources%252FMDE4NDU5MTI3NDI5MTcwNTE6NjM4NDI4MDU%253D%26cfs%3D1%26ext%3Djpg%26_nc_cb%3D1%26_nc_hash%3DAQHGXmyyiZW2XlGs&h=c1a0fa2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【Now新聞台】新冠病毒在全球大流行，原來還有另一種致命的「傳染病」在多國蔓延，香蕉飽受威脅。<br />\n<br />\n香蕉飽肚又有營養，很多人都喜歡吃，甚至把它作為主食，不過這款如此普遍的水果，原來正面臨滅種之災。這場「香蕉災難」源於一種在香蕉園肆虐的真菌&mdash;&mdash;有「香蕉癌症」之稱的黃葉病「熱帶4號」。它傳播速度很快，它能在四年內摧毀整個國家的農作物，而它並不只是毀掉香蕉，它會令香蕉再也不能在那個地方生長。<br />\n<br />\n黃葉病真菌會攻擊香蕉樹的維管系統，影響水份和有機物質的輸送，最終導致香蕉樹枯萎和死亡。而且致命的是它與新冠病毒一樣，都是隱形傳播，令人防不勝防。業界之所以如此恐懼，除了因為無藥可醫，更重要的是，真菌可於泥土存活幾十年；再加上大部分蕉農都是單一耕作，而香蕉是用無性繁殖方式種出來，令基因幾乎一模一樣，無法透過DNA變異，發展出對抗黃葉病的基因。<br />\n<br />\n目前「熱帶4號」真菌株，已經傳至全球20多個國家，連最後淨土拉丁美洲也在前年淪陷。全球很多科學家正與時間競賽，努力尋找解決方法，包括改造香蕉的基因抗黃葉病真菌。亦有研究人員認為，香蕉業要生存下去，最好還是改變種植方式，又或者引入新的品種，這樣才有望避免香蕉「末日」的來臨。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=420561&amp;fbclid=IwAR0nnNGtTMlmZXRfrxKjcplPZTZdPXWwXsMGmZF7p_pEegHkQGi15GBWoqY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D420561%26fbclid%3DIwAR0nnNGtTMlmZXRfrxKjcplPZTZdPXWwXsMGmZF7p_pEegHkQGi15GBWoqY&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHBn9kyGvuUmJUtyTBy059fc%3D&h=7419b7e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D420561%26fbclid%3DIwAR0nnNGtTMlmZXRfrxKjcplPZTZdPXWwXsMGmZF7p_pEegHkQGi15GBWoqY&h=8b38afad\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=420561&amp;fbclid=IwAR0nnNGtTMlmZXRfrxKjcplPZTZdPXWwXsMGmZF7p_pEegHkQGi15GBWoqY</a>"},{"pid":"4bf96d97f506af178cae6155985fee8141ea0bb2","tid":2369565,"uid":294343,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:03:01.000Z","msg":"我記得小學時期都有咁上下新聞，其實間中又有，一陣又米，一陣又麥"},{"pid":"11fe917051566a2de2975f839f4d3adff7066705","tid":2369565,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:03:04.000Z","msg":"世界末日喇<br />\n冇蕉吔喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a133d55989f2afae7f09d31cc84ad8f024071109","tid":2369565,"uid":15823,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:06:11.000Z","msg":"正苦，搞全蕉檢測就無事"},{"pid":"d93177b858a6842c2eed458469e13fb6e875b03c","tid":2369565,"uid":166095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:10:11.000Z","msg":"遲啲會唔會好似Interstellar咁人類主要嘅農作物逐種滅絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d85af4b535bf4b8761c6668227e9af1eac1662","tid":2369565,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:10:56.000Z","msg":"Monkey see monkey hungry"},{"pid":"2e0bcddf9ef8db19448fb7409ecc26f96ac0f97f","tid":2369565,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:12:15.000Z","msg":"左膠累事"},{"pid":"6bf532321ad8c4edc02aa8042dfa4b80ed8c9891","tid":2369565,"uid":378793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2e0bcddf9ef8db19448fb7409ecc26f96ac0f97f","tid":2369565,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:12:15.000Z","msg":"左膠累事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:13:56.000Z","msg":"人類累事"},{"pid":"c390053b41edd71639b8cd69b461bc34acd5428e","tid